---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — Mas du Chanoine" description="Privacy policy of masduchanoine.com. Information about the collection and use of your personal data." lang="en">
  <section class="relative py-20 md:py-28 px-4 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary-100"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 text-accent-600 font-light">Legal information</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-semibold text-primary-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose-content">
        <h2>Who are we?</h2>
        <p>Our website address is: <a href="https://masduchanoine.com">https://masduchanoine.com</a></p>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-serif font-semibold mb-3 mt-6 text-primary-900">Guesthouse contact details</h4>
        <p>Pascale BARISSAT – Le Mas du Chanoine<br />831 chemin de la Bastide Rouge, 06570 SAINT-PAUL DE VENCE<br />Tel: <a href="tel:+33627271649">+33 (0)6 27 27 16 49</a><br /><a href="mailto:pascale@masduchanoine.com">pascale@masduchanoine.com</a></p>
        <h2>Use of collected personal data</h2>
        <h3>Contact forms</h3>
        <p>Emails sent by prospects and clients are kept for 36 months. Client email addresses may be used once a year for greeting cards. These addresses remain confidential and are neither shared nor exchanged.</p>
        <h3>Cookies</h3>
        <p>Browsing activates Google Analytics cookies for statistical tracking. Our site also records your language preferences. You can delete these cookies in your browser settings.</p>
        <h3>Embedded content from other sites</h3>
        <p>Articles may include embedded content (videos, images, articles...). Embedded content from other sites behaves as if the visitor were visiting that other site.</p>
        <h2>Your rights over your data</h2>
        <p>You can request a file containing all personal data we hold about you. You can also request the deletion of personal data concerning you.</p>
        <h2>Contact information</h2>
        <p>For any questions about your personal data, contact us at <a href="mailto:pascale@masduchanoine.com">pascale@masduchanoine.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
